config PROPRIETARY_TI_LIBDCE
	bool "libdce 1.0.0"
	select FS_APPS_LIBDRM
	select PROPRIETARY_TI_IPC
	help 
	libdce library. 
	DCE is a library to remotely invoke the hw accellerated codecs on IVA-HD 
	via a syslink/rcm shim layer. This provides access to the codec interface 
	on the coprocessor (ducati/M3) from the host.
